data.description: Your dream farmhouse in the country is waiting for you. This home has been remodeled and upgraded with stainless appliances, granite kitchen and bathroom counters, walk-in tiled shower, hardwood floors, stone fireplace, tiled Florida room, 2 car garage, and two spacious laundry and utility rooms. The remodel also included newly installed heating and A/C unit, electrical wiring, and plumbing throughout the house. The guest bedroom is wired to function as a home office, complete with custom closet cabinetry and shelving. Additional features include a welcoming front porch and charming brick exterior fireplace.The house sits on 5 + acres located on a county maintained paved road in the country and is situated on an adjacent tract of approximately 260 acres that is a planted timber forest. Privacy is assured. The yard is spacious with beautiful trees, as well as several out buildings located on the back of the property which may serve as the perfect places to host family gatherings or to create a special he/she shed for storage and/or hobbies. You don’t want to miss the opportunity to own this peaceful paradise located in beautiful Suwannee County, just a few miles from the historic Suwannee River and numerous local fresh water springs for swimming, canoeing, fishing, or other recreational sports.
